{"tid":1977801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環大媽勁舞團違限聚令 8粉絲遭票控 3歌手獲發傳票","createTime":"2020-04-18T08:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T09:23:22.000Z","uid":7438,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fca9b0095c29b791dc82513ab6490a4a4a82ba43","tid":1977801,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:28:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200417&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60842646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200417%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60842646&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppegWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=0046d52d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200417%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60842646&h=32b909e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200417&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60842646</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情持續，當大部份市民選擇留在家中時，但一眾由屯門公園轉戰中環的大媽「勁舞團」仍無畏無懼，繼續吸金扭腰跳舞唱歌。不過，今晚7時左右，警方到中環碼頭巡查，發現大媽們繼續如常開唱，多名阿伯粉絲亦圍觀支持，由於各人的距離不足1.5米，於是警方引用《預防及控制疾病（禁止群組聚集）規例》（第599G章），票控8名阿伯粉絲，每人罰款2,000元，而3名大媽則獲傳票，各人年齡介乎38至90歲。<br />\n<br />\n詳情入apple自己睇<br />\n<br />\n抵啦 狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59036fb547c1f5bd9f4afa196fd13ef400e46da","tid":1977801,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:30:18.000Z","msg":"終於咬呢班"},{"pid":"2d9ebdbf9f6ffd8285c1d560e14ea7e3a5f1fe9a","tid":1977801,"uid":209603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fca9b0095c29b791dc82513ab6490a4a4a82ba43","tid":1977801,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:28:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200417&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60842646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.co